s%20to%20the%20best%20dog%20treats%2C%20we're%20talking%20about%20the%20healthiest%20ones%20for%20your%20dog%2C%20of%20course%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20good%20rule%20of%20thumb%20to%20follow.%20%26quot%3BThe%20simpler%2C%20the%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgoodvets.com%2Flocations%2Fcolumbus%2Fpolaris%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Kasey%20Aona%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20medical%20director%20and%20owner%20of%20GoodVets%20in%20Polaris%2C%20Ohio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20whole%2C%20unprocessed%20foods%20like%20raw%20carrots%20and%20green%20beans%2C%20commercially%20prepared%20treats%20can%20be%20convenient%20and%20healthy.%20Along%20with%20choosing%20treats%20that%20contain%20as%20few%20ingredients%20as%20possible%2C%20make%20sure%20the%20treat%20is%20safe%20for%20your%20pet%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.embracepetinsurance.com%2Fwaterbowl%2Fauthor%2Fdr-jacqueline-brister%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Jacqueline%20Brister%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20and%20consultant%20at%20Embrace%20Pet%20Insurance.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20check%20that%20the%20size%20of%20the%20treat%20isn't%20too%20big%2C%20the%20texture%20is%20right%20for%20your%20dog%2C%20your%20dog%20isn't%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvetnutrition.tufts.edu%2F2017%2F01%2Ffood-allergies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallergic%20to%20any%20of%20the%20ingredients%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20treat%20won't%20exacerbate%20health%20woes%20like%20sensitive%20teeth%20or%20weight%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20treat%20has%20cleared%20the%20safety%20inspection%2C%20the%20final%20deciding%20factor%20is%20perhaps%20the%20most%20obvious%3A%20Will%20the%20flavor%20appeal%20to%20your%20dog%3F%20Favorite%20flavors%20among%20many%20dogs%20include%20peanut%20butter%2C%20pumpkin%2C%20and%20bananas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20da