th%20private%20and%20public%20yards%20and%20will%20steadily%20expand%20into%20other%20shipbuilding%20programs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20is%20pouring%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20into%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20system%20that%20it%20says%20has%20sped%20up%20key%20shipbuilding%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20case%2C%20the%20AI%20cut%20painstaking%20processes%20of%20submarine%20schedule%20planning%20%E2%80%94%20mapping%20out%20how%20the%20many%20pieces%20of%20construction%20fit%20together%20and%20making%20sure%20people%2C%20parts%2C%20and%20yard%20space%20are%20available%20at%20the%20right%20time%20%E2%80%94%20from%20many%20hours%20to%20only%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20is%20launching%20the%20new%20Shipbuilding%20Operating%20System%2C%20or%20Ship%20OS%2C%20as%20it%20tries%20to%20break%20out%20of%20decades-old%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnavy-cancels-future-constellation-class-frigates-raising-fleet-size-concerns-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20shipbuilding%20problems%3C%2Fa%3E%20rooted%20in%20outdated%20technologies%20and%20work%20practices.%20The%20service%20announced%20a%20%24448%20million%20investment%20Thursday%2C%20saying%20it%20will%20accelerate%20the%20adoption%20of%20AI%20and%20autonomy%20across%20the%20industrial%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ship%20OS%20technology%20is%20powered%20by%20Palantir's%20Foundry%20and%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20Platform%20and%20began%20in%20pilot%20programs%20at%20submarine%20shipyards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20General%20Dynamics%20Electric%20Boat%2C%20a%20long-time%20submarine%20yard%20located%20in%20Connecticut%2C%20submarine%20schedule%20planning%20saw%20a%20dramatic%20reduction%20from%20160%20manual%20hours%20down%20to%20under%2010%20minutes.%20And%20at%20Portsmouth%20Naval%20Shipyard%20in%20Maine%2C%20material%20review%20times%20for%20submarines%20went%20from%20taking%20weeks%20to%20under%20an%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%24448%